<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1951-12-08T13:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1951-12-08T13:00:00-05:00" n="516" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d516">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–851: Telegram</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The United States Representative at the United
                                    Nations</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Austin</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#left">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">restricted</hi>
                                    <lb/>
                                    <gloss target="#t_niact1">
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                                    </gloss>
                                </seg>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1951-12-08T19:00:00+01:00">December 8, 1951—7 p.m.</date>
                                </dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 573. Re joint resolution on
                                self-determination (<gloss target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 564, Dec
                                8), staff intends recommend <gloss target="#t_USGADel1">USGADel</gloss> take following action in Committee Three Monday
                                morning, Dec 10: <list>
                                    <label>(1)</label>
                                    <item>Speak in favor of general principle of self-determination
                                        as related to nonself-governing territories, countries which
                                        have lost their independence in recent years and countries
                                        whose independence may be threatened.</item>
                                    <pb facs="0798" n="776" xml:id="pg_776"/>
                                    <label>(2)</label>
                                    <item>Introduce following amendment to operative paragraph: <list>
                                            <item>“Decides to include a provision in the
                                                International Covenant on Human Rights recognizing
                                                the principle of self-determination of peoples
                                                enunciated in the Charter of the United
                                                Nations.”</item>
                                        </list>
                                    </item>
                                </list>
                            </p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Austin</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>